{"tid":1364914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港條龍脈俾人打斷左  大家有得走好走啦","createTime":"2019-07-25T13:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T06:13:31.000Z","uid":259010,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5242149f2a5d99c88c4fc6156746cf5fc3597eb3","tid":1364914,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:03:08.000Z","msg":"今日西九打斷左香港條龍脈<img src=\"http://www.as2.net/data/attach/1703/g1bJ9yXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.as2.net%2Fdata%2Fattach%2F1703%2Fg1bJ9yXq.jpg&h=4b0d60b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f14daa7012310e3cb344335b5ec4ee3731afd638","tid":1364914,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:04:05.000Z","msg":"條脈都頂你地唔順自爆左"},{"pid":"0923fdb3d4de629db12774a6fc2320c6a10f3bed","tid":1364914,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"再加大學單野<br />\n<br />\n香港40年大運要轉運啦"},{"pid":"f689511b7fb4f093aba0f45d3c71b5b8d94320b4","tid":1364914,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊出唔出元朗好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"15bf077364b47263b9b1ec34176c706a194d58f2","tid":1364914,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"點解今日"},{"pid":"6f100e67ea12adb2c43515c83f8bac79d0acb68b","tid":1364914,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"詳細分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06a09bf29fcccb8fe94c7b72ef547d0cef926ca","tid":1364914,"uid":60434,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:06:22.000Z","msg":"真正行好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時代革命"},{"pid":"37cf1c4816957711ee55e15385ad088cb8f32f1f","tid":1364914,"uid":33408,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:07:15.000Z","msg":"咩話 近平條巨龍斷撚左<br />\n咁咪變太監平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2de1ed8f831261635f98988ace7252dbf27191f","tid":1364914,"uid":259010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"「九龍」之名來自風水 <br />\n相傳遠古時代，香港還未命名，有一位風水先生為尋找風水寶地，穿州過省，南下來到香港半島，站在大概是現今禮賓府（前身為港督府）一帶，隔着維多利亞港北望九龍半島的獅子山、筆架山和飛鵝山，發現此三山共有九條龍脈向着香港半島奔跑過來，一起一伏，非常大吉，令人拍案叫絕，故即時以「九龍」命名此風水奇地。<br />\n交通總站最聚氣 <br />\n龍由山上奔下，龍頭停頓之位置龍氣最旺盛，亦稱結聚點；以現代觀點來看，各交通交滙點或大型的交通工具總站，皆龍氣結聚之處。<br />\n<br />\n龍頭聚氣大吉昌 <br />\n龍為中國的吉祥之物，傳統的風水學認為，龍脈，乃地裏的「生氣」。因此龍脈所經之處，尤其是停頓的地方，便是「生氣」（或稱龍氣）結聚之地，在此居住，旺丁旺財，大吉大利。<br />\n九條龍脈分布圖 <br />\n以下是九龍半島的龍脈走勢，請看圖索驥。謹記，龍氣結聚地最旺，所經之處亦有旺氣到。 <br />\n<br />\n〈第一條龍〉 <br />\n筆架山&rarr;李鄭屋邨&rarr;蘇屋村古墓&rarr;蘇屋邨 <br />\n〈第二條龍〉 <br />\n筆架山&rarr;石硤尾&rarr;深水埗&rarr;大角嘴 <br />\n〈第三條龍〉 <br />\n筆架山&rarr;石硤尾&rarr;太子&rarr;旺角 <br />\n〈第四條龍〉 <br />\n筆架山&rarr;歌和老街&rarr;九龍塘&rarr;何文田&rarr;佐敦&rarr;尖沙嘴 <br />\n〈第五條龍〉 <br />\n獅子山&rarr;樂富&rarr;廣播道&rarr;九龍仔公園&rarr;馬頭圍道&rarr;紅磡 <br />\n〈第六條龍〉 <br />\n獅子山&rarr;九龍城&rarr;宋皇台&rarr;土瓜灣 <br />\n〈第七條龍〉 <br />\n獅子山&rarr;龍翔道&rarr;黃大仙 <br />\n〈第八條龍〉 <br />\n飛鵝山&rarr;鑽石山&rarr;牛頭角 <br />\n〈第九條龍〉 <br />\n飛鵝山&rarr;斧山&rarr;牛池灣&rarr;彩虹"},{"pid":"15e0006b6913df33a40f65122061fcbb84b82b06","tid":1364914,"uid":259010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:06:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68890fc0b5745b7d217cd77e356799b3839eee23","tid":1364914,"uid":27946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}